The Terminal Weakling<br>
High Elf Enchanter<br>
<br>
P.S. ... I cast Augment on everyone in the group... don't care if they use it or not... it's just such a nifty spell. I also often cast my charisma buffs on folks ... a bit of an instant makeover. Tanks generally get Clarity, too, mostly because they hate it so much (especially rogues, for some reason). I'm sure once I get my Intelligence buffs I'll cast them to make a point.<br>
<br>
The spells you use and how you use them can be as much a part of your character as the way you speak, especially as an echanter. Illusions are one of the reasons I chose this class on this server. <br>
